f = BaseOutputFile('test.csv')
f.add_row([1, 2])
f.write_to_file()
with open(f.file_path, 'r') as tf:
    assert '1,2\n' == tf.read()
f.headers = ['First', 'Second']
assert f.write_to_file()
with open(f.file_path, 'r') as tf:
    assert '"First","Second"\n1,2\n' == tf.read()
os.remove(f.file_path)
